menu "HAL Configuration"

    config HAL_IMU_USE_BNO08X
        bool "Enable BNO08x IMU driver (requires esp32_BNO08x component)"
        default n
        help
            When enabled, hal_imu.c compiles with the real BNO085 SPI backend.
            When disabled, hal_imu returns stub data (yaw=0) so the project
            builds without the third-party component.

endmenu